And there is only one carrier for the transfer of energy to millions of reactions per second and to<br>
each cell - this is unheated photons. A coherent photon field is the source of such photons.<br>
Therefore a weak flow of photons from a biological object, which is well known at present and<br>
includes the whole spectrum of radiation from ultraviolet to infrared, is called with biophotons<br>
and may be quite sufficient to carry out the role of controlling the biochemistry and biology of a<br>
live organism.<br>
The therrnoluminescence, or more exactly - thermostimulated luminescence,<br>
