The device operates in the following manner. At first information is recorded in a<br>
memory on the metabolic activity of deposited cells, changed in any known manner. With the<br>
aid of the unit for changing temperature, a single element is heated. Wherein information on a<br>
changed metabolic activity of deposited cells at a bioresonant frequency is recorded in the<br>
