irradiated is set similar to that deposited with a changed metabolic activity. In order to maintain<br>
the predetermined metabolic activity of the cells being irradiated for a lengthy period of time,<br>
repeated sessions of irradiation are carried out at certain intervals of time.<br>
The device does not provide a high degree of inactivation of pathogenic microorganisms<br>
